#VGOn24",0 Codes Left - https://matcherino.com/tournaments/116743 - DDP - SA - (Cross-Platform),True,True,reciQG6zb8MnJVzCx,Week 2,https://www.start.gg/tournament/vortex-gallery-online-2024-1/event/dodonpachi-daioujou-sa,mandaloris,4,3,https://v5.airtableusercontent.com/v3/u/43/43/1753617600000/on-nr4SJmYfaoonuDLjGQQ/WXhYBcBkiEqfiG9FcYfVve3-tggWYlEoIQJ6goGTTtY_g2wTu9NoEyueeP3KedFCcAVZgbmD56fDhHat7NBgBlVPNDtfyWq_fuETNIrdoQ_nVwHWh9jcpv19p7OfYtvm6YvSZhSiZL5jF18m0KYUWvLo-6KVfvxsoTGQmbQPB9g/GskW3CHUP48y83gUMSdqICT_-9Z6ZYTPPadwHWttz0I,,"Players have 20 minutes to play and restart the game as many times as they want. After 20 minutes pass, they can't restart anymore and have to play through completion or until they lose all their lives. Their score for the last run is then submitted to leaderboard.

Players may choose to stop playing during the first 20 minutes if they manage to get a clear.

As long as the Black Label version is respected, players can choose to play the game on whichever platform they want (arcade PCB, Xbox 360, PS4, Switch and emulation). Just be sure to have the means to share the screen through VDO.Ninja and Discord.",,,Every player must share their game screen through VDO.Ninja (https://vdo.ninja/) AND Discord.,"- Must be played on Black Label version (2002.10.07.BLACK VER);
