VDO.ninja so the match can be streamed: https://vdo.ninja/",,,,"I couldn't find VividSniper on the list of volunteers to put down as head TO/bracket runner. Still working/finalizing on other staff, especially for commentary and bracket runners.

Not 100% final with the scheduling yet, will double-check with the other staff/maybe-staff, but tentatively this should work. I don't think we are super particular with the date/time, we should be able to work around what we're given.",True,recRndBbmGuBJn7jo,True,True,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
